      <title>加息对日本经济造成冲击，投资者看重长期前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/investors-take-long-term-view-as-rate-hike-whipsaws-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周日本加息令基准指数遭受八年来最大冲击。尽管市场动荡，但部分投资者仍对日本股市的长期前景充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/investors-take-long-term-view-as-rate-hike-whipsaws-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
